column3: Traffic Alert for Man O War Blvd:
column4: Police activity in the area of Man O War Blvd and Crosby Dr.
The roadway is shutdown at the bridge over KY-1665 (Evergreen Rd) until approximately 3 p.m. for bridge deck repairs.
Motorists may detour using Exit 53B (US-127) -> US-60W -> left onto KY-151S -> back to I-64W.
